	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Game Genie multi-codes?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you want to see what the original game genie UI looked like, an NROM version of that is available on this site:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/genie.zip">http://nesdev.com/genie.zip</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Some people do actually chain multiple game genies to implement more codes, though, so in practice the limitations of the hardware have been occasionally exceeded in that way.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


