	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Game Genie multi-codes?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I don't know what happens if you add two codes patching the same address.</div> When I <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=14573&amp;p=175908#p175928" class="postlink">examined the writes</a> the Game Genie ROM uses to send the codes to its hardware, the results I saw suggested the following: If you enter multiple codes for the same address, the Game Genie only uses the first one and marks the others as invalid/disabled.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
